superstudio is a boutique production studio founded in 2007 by Dana Garman. The roster includes Directors Ty Evans, Johannes Gamble, Jona Frank, Dewey Nicks and Tilford. Credits include ESPN, Nike, Mitsubishi and Mountain Dew.
superstudio produced an interactive campaign for Nissan Rogue, winning a shortlist for The Cannes Lions Awards, Best Interactive at The ad:tech Interactive Awards and a Best in Show and three Golds at The MIXX Awards.
